&lt;h3 id=&#34;day-4---day-3-on-the-mountain&#34;&gt;Day 4 - Day 3 on the mountain&lt;/h3&gt;





  











&lt;figure &gt;


  &lt;a data-fancybox=&#34;&#34; href=&#34;/img/rinjani/PANO_20161207_180131-L.jpg&#34; &gt;


