&lt;h3 id=&#34;day-4--5---day-3--4-on-the-mountain&#34;&gt;Day 4 &amp;amp; 5 - Day 3 &amp;amp; 4 on the mountain&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We camped on the Senaru side of the crater rim for the night. It was the first night on the mountain where it was not windy. This gave us the opportunity to set up the tripods for some long exposure photography.&lt;/p&gt;





  











