&lt;p&gt;We woke up around 2 or 3 AM and were greeted with the most beautiful sight we had seen. Our Galaxy Milky Way in it&amp;rsquo;s full glory. Unfortunately, we did not take out the cameras to click any pictures since we wanted to have enough rest for the next day&amp;rsquo;s long descent.&lt;/p&gt;





  











